text:
<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
We are investigating errors and latencies on IAM Console and APIs in the US-GOV-WEST-1 Region. Users may experience delays or failures in the creation or modification of IAM entities such as users, roles and policies. Authentication and authorizations using existing IAM entities are not impacted.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
Between 5:08 AM and 7:15 AM PDT we experienced increased errors and latencies on IAM Console and APIs in the US-GOV-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
